Flying, ward {2}
[i]Landfall[/i] – Whenever a land you control enters, exile the top card of your library and a card from your graveyard and put a link counter on each of them.
Whenever Jwar Isle Riddler deals combat damage to a player, mill two cards. Then if there are five or more different mana values among cards you own in exile with link counters on them, you win the game.
